        Selling a Strata Title Property in Brisbane: What Owners Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Units and townhouses in Brisbane's inner east come with a layer of body corporate documentation and disclosure that house sales don't require. Here is what to gather and what buyers will scrutinise.
      </p>
